20:33.566 --> 20:34.818
[thumps door]

21:22.364 --> 21:23.364
[lock turns]

22:33.519 --> 22:36.273
[glass screeches]

22:36.355 --> 22:37.356
[sound fades out]

22:40.193 --> 22:41.569
[glass screeches]

23:20.275 --> 23:21.483
[air hisses]

23:32.037 --> 23:33.246
[air hisses]

25:53.635 --> 25:54.845
Can you read my lips?

26:03.562 --> 26:04.562
Can you?

26:13.406 --> 26:15.574
You have seen it now, haven't you?

26:25.543 --> 26:26.794
"Seriously, Maddie.

26:26.877 --> 26:29.506
Maybe you could come back
and live with me."

26:30.215 --> 26:31.590
"You know, I worry about you.

26:31.673 --> 26:34.094
It's not good for anyone to be so alone,
Squish."

26:39.349 --> 26:41.559
I can come in any time I want.

26:42.893 --> 26:44.895
And I can get you any time I want.

26:46.564 --> 26:47.689
But I'm not going to.

26:48.941 --> 26:49.942
Not until it's time.

26:51.236 --> 26:53.028
When you wish you are dead -

26:53.113 --> 26:54.655
that's when I'll come inside.

26:57.074 --> 26:58.201
Do you understand me?

27:02.247 --> 27:04.457
Nod your head if you understand me.

27:11.214 --> 27:12.214
Good.

27:15.759 --> 27:17.010
Then we can have some fun.

27:20.931 --> 27:21.931
Enjoy it.

27:44.872 --> 27:45.873
